===Etymology===
From ''[[blood]]'' and ''[[mobile]],'' the latter a common [[suffix]] in [[w:English language|English]] [[compound word]]s of which are [[related]] to [[automobilia]]. Coined in [[w:1948|1948]].

===Noun===
'''bloodmobile'''
# A [[vehicle]] of which [[collect]]s blood from [[donor]]s.

